  "text": "On the other hand, EVs have been also proposed as new forms of treatment for different diseases, given that EVs are natural systems able to deliver biological messages to target cells. The goal of the research in this field is to substitute the biological messages into therapeutic molecules. To achieve this goal, different aspects should be taken into account, such as the improvement of biotechnology techniques, the choice of EV cellular source, loading, isolation methods, and engineering approaches for drug targeting [CITATION_1] .",
